       "data": "Out[215]= -\\frac{z^{\\frac{\\theta1+\\theta2}{h}-\\frac{\\theta1}{h}-\\frac{\\theta2}{h}}\\,\\left(z\\,f\\left(h+\\theta1\\right)\\,\\left(f\\left(\\theta2\\right)\\,\\left(h-\\theta1+\\theta2\\right)+z\\,\\left(\\theta1-\\theta2\\right)\\,f\\left(h+\\theta2\\right)\\right)+f\\left(\\theta1\\right)\\,\\left(f\\left(\\theta2\\right)\\,\\left(\\theta1-\\theta2\\right)-z\\,f\\left(h+\\theta2\\right)\\,\\left(h+\\theta1-\\theta2\\right)\\right)\\right)}{f\\left(\\theta1\\right)\\,f\\left(\\theta2\\right)\\,\\left(\\theta2-\\theta1\\right)}",
